          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add your<strong> finely</strong> <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong>, <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>and <strong>dried oregano</strong></p><p>Cook for a further 3-4 min or until it's slightly thickened</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
