    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sauce has slightly thickened, add the <strong>salmon flakes</strong></p><p>Season with a generous grind of <strong>pepper </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until the salmon is warmed through</p>",
      "order": 6,
